{
  "stem": "1641.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, after four, six weeks, they died from hunger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they always got filled up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when you throw out three bodies, doesn't mean that you had the place to yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the evening, it was full up again with-- with thicker and fat-- I mean, relatively speaking, not so starved people as we were.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's-- that's how the time went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went-- we went through these months, February, March.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only good thing was that the SS man left his paper with the chief Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Doctor-- I mean, but he could do two things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, he left his SS paper there, the [GERMAN], the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we could read that the German troops achieved a big victory, holding back the enemy at Vienna, [LAUGHS] and always winning, of course with-- with big defeat on the Russian forces.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We killed several thousand west of Vienna-- east of Vienna, and then west of Vienna, and then next-- next to Breslau, and 100 miles from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we could see what-- what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Americans suffered a terrific defeat on crossing the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we knew that they crossed the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they had a big defeat at some other place near Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Germans were always winning, naturally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were always big victories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Fuhrer always promised the final surprise weapon, daily.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was the V1, the V2.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And wait until the V-- that was the atomic bomb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he couldn't make it in time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One more year, and he would have had it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so the V1 and V2, already killing thousands of Englishmen, which was true.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said, the V3 is coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
